OL,3,CThree arrests over 'distressing'
OL,4,Cclaims of grave interference
OL,6,FThree men have been arrested after an
OL,7,Feight-day investigation into
OL,8,F"distressing" claims that a grave was
OL,9,Fdisturbed at a South Yorkshire
OL,10,Fcemetery.
OL,12,FOfficers were called to All Saints
OL,13,FChurch, in Laughton-en-le-Morthen,
OL,14,Fnear Rotherham after a reported crime
OL,15,Fon 1 February.
OL,17,FThe church yard remained closed for
OL,18,Fthe next eight days but has now
OL,19,Freopened.
