OL,3,CThree arrests over 'distressing'
OL,4,Cclaims of grave interference
OL,6,F"I would like to thank everyone for
OL,7,Ftheir support and understanding around
OL,8,Fthis sensitive matter, especially
OL,9,Fthose who could not visit the church
OL,10,Fyard during this time.
OL,12,F"Our investigation is continuing into
OL,13,Fthis incident, but I want to provide
OL,14,Freassurance that we believe that this
OL,15,Fwas a targeted incident and that there
OL,16,Fis no threat to other graves."
